    <name>Assignment #2: Do a Quick Write with students and reflect</name>
    <intro>&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Introduce Quick Writes to your students. They can help adult learners become comfortable with writing and build their writing fluency.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In one week, assign two or more Quick Writes so students get familiar with them.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Collect a couple of student samples and hold a mini-workshop with at least one student to discuss his or her thoughts on the process.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Write a two- to three-paragraph reflection of what you learned (click Add or Edit my submission).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</intro>
